ecret."}, {"version": "emerald", "text": "Usually docile, a WOBBUFFET strikes back ferociously if its black tail is attacked. It makes its lair in caves where it waits for nightfall."}, {"version": "firered", "text": "To keep its pitch-black tail hidden, it lives quietly in the darkness. It is never first to attack."}, {"version": "gold", "text": "It hates light and shock. If attack\u00ad ed, it inflates its body to pump up its counter\u00ad strike."}, {"version": "heartgold", "text": "It hates light and shock. If attacked, it inflates its body to build up its counterstrike."}, {"version": "leafgreen", "text": "It hates light and shock. If attacked, it inflates its body to pump up its counterstrike."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "If two or more Wobbuffet meet, they will turn competitive and try to outdo each other\u2019s endurance. However, they may try to see which one can endure the longest without food. Trainers need to beware of this habit."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "It desperately tries to keep its black tail hidden. It is said to be proof the tail hides a secret."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "It desperately tries to keep its black tail hidden. It is said to be proof the tail hides a secret."}, {"version": "ruby", "text": "If two or more WOBBUFFET meet, they will turn competitive and try to outdo each other\u2019s endurance. However, they may try to see which one can endure the longest without food. TRAINERS need to beware of this habit."}, {"version": "sapphire", "text": "WOBBUFFET does nothing but endure attacks - it won\u2019t attack on its own. However, it won\u2019t endure an attack on its tail. When that happens, the POK\u00e9MON will try to take the foe with it using DESTINY BOND."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "To keep its pitch-black tail hidden, it lives quietly in the darkness. It is never first to attack."}, {"version": "silver", "text": "To keep its pitch- black tail hidden, it lives quietly in the darkness. It is never first t